  "title": "Nat & Chrissy: Everything is on the Table",
  "description": "A high-energy duo serving up cheeky humour, delightfully absurd concepts, and an abundance of laughs. You know them from beloved Edmonton fixtures Weird Al Karaoke and Blue Halloo Comedy. Now, Nat &amp; Chrissy invite you to join them for a truly playful sketch comedy experience.",
  "credits": "<strong>Cast</strong>: Nathalie Feehan &amp; Christine DeWitt<br/>",
